NK010(tha)021:1: sri gnon rgya gram nag po bzhugs /
NK010(tha)021:2: bcom ldan 'das mthu stobs kyi dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)021:3: rdo rje phur pa'i sgo nas sri gnon pa'i thabs la sbyor dngos rjes gsum las /
NK010(tha)021:6: rgyal po phung ba'i phung sri ni //
NK010(tha)021:7: mon dang hor mo spyi ring mgor //
NK010(tha)021:8: chos 'khor dbus su gnan par bya //
NK010(tha)021:9: yang na yul gyi mdo nyid do //
NK010(tha)021:10: dgra sri rta g.yag thod pa ru //
NK010(tha)021:11: dgra zun mtshams su gnan par bya //
NK010(tha)021:12: dam sri g.yi spyang thod pa ru //
NK010(tha)021:13: grong gi dbus su gnan par bya //
NK010(tha)021:14: blon po phung ba'i phung sri ni //
NK010(tha)021:15: spre'u'am ne tsho pha wang thod //
NK010(tha)021:17: yul khams phung ba'i phung sri ni //
NK010(tha)021:18: mdzo rtol dre'u'i thod pa ru //
NK010(tha)021:19: yul gyi dbus su gnan par bya //
NK010(tha)021:20: dme yis phung ba'i phung sri ni //
NK010(tha)021:21: g.yi dang gsa' spyang thod pa ru //
NK010(tha)021:22: grong brdal chen po'i dbus su mnan //
NK010(tha)021:23: chung sri khyi phag thod pa ru //
NK010(tha)021:24: mal gyi 'og tu gnan par bya //
NK010(tha)021:25: dur sri wa thod grum thod dam //
NK010(tha)021:26: yang na zer mo'i thod pa ru //
NK010(tha)021:27: dur gyi 'dabs su gnan par bya //
NK010(tha)021:28: rnal 'byor dam sri mi dang khyi //
NK010(tha)021:29: phag thod la sogs snod du ni //
NK010(tha)021:30: mchod rten 'og tu gnan par bya //
NK010(tha)021:31: god sri ra lug thod pa ru //
NK010(tha)021:32: ra ba'i dbus su gnan par bya //
NK010(tha)021:33: zhes pas snod dang gnas bstan cing /
NK010(tha)021:34: de'i nang du sri can so so'i ling+ga bca' tshul ni /
NK010(tha)021:35: 'khor lo rtsibs drug bris pa la //
NK010(tha)021:36: dbus su sri dang tri bri'o //
NK010(tha)021:37: dgra la byed na n+ri yang bri //
NK010(tha)021:38: rtsibs drug la ni sngags drug bri //
NK010(tha)021:39: mtha' ma khro bcu'i sngags kyis bskor //
NK010(tha)021:40: dbus kyi lte bar gzugs bris la //
NK010(tha)021:41: snying gar rus la dpral bar ming //
NK010(tha)021:42: yan lag bzhi la yig 'bru bzhi //
NK010(tha)021:43: m+aa ra ya yis mtha' ma bskor //
NK010(tha)021:44: sngo dmar dkri zhing re bas gtum //
NK010(tha)021:45: zhes pas 'khor lo mu khyud gsum pa'i lte bar
NK010(tha)021:46: dgra sri ma gtogs sri can gyi ling+ga thams cad
NK010(tha)021:47: mi gzugs bya mchu can gyi snying gar dgra la
NK010(tha)021:48: n+ri dang / gzhan rnams la tri yig dza sprod
NK010(tha)021:49: kyi bar du gtems pa'i mtha' skor du dzahh+aum bam
NK010(tha)021:50: hohmo ha g+ha ya che ge mo badz+ra ang+ku sha
NK010(tha)021:51: dzah che ge mo h+aum dzah zhes pas bskor /
NK010(tha)021:52: dpral bar sri can gang yin gyi ming spel bcug pa'i mnan sngags dper na /
NK010(tha)021:53: lam h+aum lam rgyal po phung ba'i phung sri s+t+wam+b+ha nan /
NK010(tha)021:55: yan lag bzhi la dzahh+aum bam hoh gzugs kyi mtha' skor du m+aa ra ya nan rnams bri /
NK010(tha)021:56: mu khyud gnyis par 'khor lo rtsibs drug gi mgo thog nas rim par g.yas bskor du /
NK010(tha)021:57: ha sa ya ra sogs sngags drug po bri /
NK010(tha)021:58: mu khyud gsum par khro bcu'i sngags mthar che ge mo s+t+wam+b+ha nan /
NK010(tha)021:60: phyi rol dza khram gyis bskor /
NK010(tha)021:61: d+ha du ra dang dug khrag gis byugs /
NK010(tha)021:62: gtor zlog dang 'brel na zor gtor gyi 'og tu
NK010(tha)021:63: bye stegs kyi brub khung nang du bcug gal te
NK010(tha)021:64: sri gnon rkyang pa byed na lcags kyi hom khung
NK010(tha)021:65: ngam / sla nga bye mas bkang bar brub khung
NK010(tha)021:66: brus pa'i nang du ling+ga bcug la kha khyer rtsang
NK010(tha)021:67: gis srin mo 'gros su bskor ba'i steng bsnyen phur
NK010(tha)021:69: ske shang nyung dkar lcags zangs phye la dug khrag gis ngar btags pa'i thun rdzas dang /
NK010(tha)021:70: mnan snod phung re sogs kyang tshogs par bya'o //
NK010(tha)021:72: bsnyen bsgrub gdab las tshul bzhin bya //
NK010(tha)021:73: zor dang hom dang mnan pa dang //
NK010(tha)021:74: tha mas las su grub pa yin //
NK010(tha)021:75: zhes pa'i don las dang po bsnyen bsgrub ni /
NK010(tha)021:76: stegs mtho bar yi dam dang chos srung gi mchod gtor tshogs par byas la /
NK010(tha)021:77: sgrub thabs 'bring bsdus gang rigs kyi gzhung srong nas bzlas pa ci nus bya'o //
NK010(tha)021:79: gtor zlog dang 'brel na gzu dpang dang /
NK010(tha)021:81: bzhi snying dril ba'i bzlas pa gsum gyi mjug tu
NK010(tha)021:82: bla 'gugs kyi pho nya mo bzhi'i sgos bskul dang
NK010(tha)021:83: sri can 'gugs pa'i sngags ci nus re spel nas
NK010(tha)021:85: gal te sri mnan rkyang pa byed na /
NK010(tha)021:86: dam can mchod bskul bsdus pa byas la /
NK010(tha)021:87: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ka tam ka ye dza ye bi dza ye /
NK010(tha)021:88: a tsi te a pa ra tsi te /
NK010(tha)021:89: ma ra s+ya na pra marta ni ye sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:90: ces brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas so //
NK010(tha)021:91: de nas bla 'gugs kyi pho nya mo bzhi bskul ba ni /
NK010(tha)021:93: dpal gyi pho nya las mkhan mo //
NK010(tha)021:94: dkar mo dung gi mche ba can //
NK010(tha)021:96: lag na spu gris sems can sgrol //
NK010(tha)021:97: zhal du dgra bo'i snying khrag rngub //
NK010(tha)021:98: sprul pa thog thog ser chen 'bebs //
NK010(tha)021:99: pho nya sum brgya drug cu 'gyed //
NK010(tha)021:100: sum brgya drug cu'i gtso mo ste //
NK010(tha)021:101: bskal pa brgyad khri'i pha rol nas //
NK010(tha)021:103: nyams pa'i bla la nan ma chung //
NK010(tha)021:104: lho yi phyogs nas 'byung ba ni //
NK010(tha)021:105: nag mo lcags kyi lan tshar can //
NK010(tha)021:106: khyung gi khra thogs g.yas pa na //
NK010(tha)021:107: b+han+d+ha gri thogs gsod la rngams //
NK010(tha)021:108: tshangs pa bsgyings pa'i cha lugs can //
NK010(tha)021:109: mi sdug mgo la gcer bu'i lus //
NK010(tha)021:110: pho nya sum brgya drug cu 'gyed //
NK010(tha)021:111: su cu drug cu'i gtso mo ste //
NK010(tha)021:112: bskal pa brgyad nas bla tshol tshol //
NK010(tha)021:114: nyams pa'i bla dang srog la ya //
NK010(tha)021:115: nub kyi phyogs nas 'byung ba ni //
NK010(tha)021:117: gdug pa 'dul la drag po ste //
NK010(tha)021:118: gsod la rngams pa'i las la brtson //
NK010(tha)021:119: mche gtsigs g.yang gzhi gos su gyon //
NK010(tha)021:120: sum brgya drug cu'i gtso mo ste //
NK010(tha)021:121: rab tu bsgrubs nas bla 'gugs ma //
NK010(tha)021:122: nyams pa'i bla dang srog la ya //
NK010(tha)021:123: byang gi phyogs nas 'byung ba ni //
NK010(tha)021:124: ljang nag 'khyil ba'i thod gdengs can //
NK010(tha)021:125: ser mo ral can 'bum gyis bskor //
NK010(tha)021:126: phyag na ral gri gsod la rngams //
NK010(tha)021:127: sum brgya drug cu'i gtso mo ste //
NK010(tha)021:128: sngon nas sri can bla 'gugs ma //
NK010(tha)021:129: nyams pa'i bla dang srog la ya //
NK010(tha)021:130: nam mkha'i lha mo phur pa'i lha //
NK010(tha)021:131: lag brgya lcags kyi phur pa 'dril //
NK010(tha)021:132: spyan brgya khrag gi mchi ma 'dzag /
NK010(tha)021:133: zhal brgya gdug pa'i ngan sngags zlos //
NK010(tha)021:134: tshems kyis skye shi rtsa ba gcod //
NK010(tha)021:135: phur pa'i las mkhan chen mo ma //
NK010(tha)021:136: rab tu mi bsrun las la brtson //
NK010(tha)021:137: pho nya mang po phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NK010(tha)021:138: rdo rje sku gsung thugs las sprul //
NK010(tha)021:139: nyams pa'i bla dang srog la ya //
NK010(tha)021:142: dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah rgyal sri h+aum
NK010(tha)021:143: dzah zhes pas mtshon bargya'am stong phrag re'i mtshams su
NK010(tha)021:144: pho nya bskul ba ci nus bya'o //
NK010(tha)021:145: de nas zan ling re bsham la phyi dro'i thun la gdab las re bya ba'i /
NK010(tha)021:148: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)021:149: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)021:150: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)021:151: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)021:152: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)021:153: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)021:154: khyed kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK010(tha)021:155: mthu rtsal 'byung ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)021:156: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)021:157: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)021:158: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK010(tha)021:159: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK010(tha)021:160: zungs shig chings shig rnam par chings //
NK010(tha)021:161: rengs par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK010(tha)021:162: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlogs //
NK010(tha)021:163: nga yi dbang du gyur nas ni //
NK010(tha)021:164: bsgo ba'i bka' rnams nyan par gyis //
NK010(tha)021:166: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hohche ge
NK010(tha)021:167: mo ha sa ya ra hri tan a be sha
NK010(tha)021:169: shi kri a na ya shi kri a na ya /
NK010(tha)021:170: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya /
NK010(tha)021:171: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya /
NK010(tha)021:172: ban+d+ha ya b+han+d+ha ya sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:176: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)021:177: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK010(tha)021:178: phung po rdo rjes gtams byas nas //
NK010(tha)021:179: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK010(tha)021:180: lam h+aum lam s+t+wam b+ha nan /
NK010(tha)021:181: mo ha g+ha ya b+ha ga w+aa na shi kri
NK010(tha)021:182: bi kri sh+ri badz+ra h+aum k+aa ra h+aum h+aum phata
NK010(tha)021:185: bdag cag rnal 'byor sgrub pa pos //
NK010(tha)021:186: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK010(tha)021:187: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung gsob pa'i //
NK010(tha)021:188: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK010(tha)021:189: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK010(tha)021:190: bdud dang bar du gcod pa dang //
NK010(tha)021:191: dngos grub phrog cing 'tshe ba rnams //
NK010(tha)021:192: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK010(tha)021:193: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir khug la //
NK010(tha)021:194: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang //
NK010(tha)021:195: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlogs //
NK010(tha)021:196: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)021:197: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la dzahh+aum bam hohha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:198: da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:199: pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:200: ma tha ma tha h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:201: dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:202: su ru su ru h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:203: mu ru mu ru h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:204: ka tang ka te h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:205: dza ye bi dza ye h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:206: a tsi te a pa ra tsi te ma ra
NK010(tha)021:207: sa na pra marta na ye sarba big nan bam
NK010(tha)021:209: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)021:210: lha'am gnod sbyin bdud kyang rung //
NK010(tha)021:211: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK010(tha)021:212: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par mdzod //
NK010(tha)021:213: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh pa ra big nan sarba big tan h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:216: g+h+ri ha na g+h+ri ha na h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:217: ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:218: da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:220: sarba a na ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:221: lnga pa bsad gris gzir zhing /
NK010(tha)021:223: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)021:224: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)021:225: sngon chad ji ltar dam bcas pa'i //
NK010(tha)021:226: mngon spyod phrin las myur du mdzod //
NK010(tha)021:227: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ma tha ma tha badz+ra /
NK010(tha)021:231: sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:232: drug pa thun dbab pa ni /
NK010(tha)021:234: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK010(tha)021:235: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK010(tha)021:236: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK010(tha)021:237: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK010(tha)021:238: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK010(tha)021:239: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK010(tha)021:240: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la dzahh+aum bam hoh ka tang ka te /
NK010(tha)021:242: a tsi te a pa ra tsi te /
NK010(tha)021:243: ma ra s+yee na pra marta ni ya h+aum ma
NK010(tha)021:244: ma p+aa sham ku ru ma tang nya ka ra
NK010(tha)021:245: i nan d+ha ti ma ma karma sh+ai kram ka
NK010(tha)021:246: ra ya sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)021:247: bdun pa gtun du brdung ba ni /
NK010(tha)021:249: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK010(tha)021:250: bka' las 'da' byed sdig can rnams //
NK010(tha)021:251: rdo rje me dbal snying bsreg nas //
NK010(tha)021:252: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlogs //
NK010(tha)021:253: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK010(tha)021:254: rdo rje tho bas brdung byas nas //
NK010(tha)021:255: lha yang rung ste brlag par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)021:260: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)021:261: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)021:262: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK010(tha)021:263: bsgo ba'i bka' ni nyan par byos //
NK010(tha)021:266: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)021:268: gal te gtor zlog dang 'brel na zlog pa'i phrin las gzhung bsrangs nas /
NK010(tha)021:269: thun gtor 'phang ba yan chad nyin ltar bya'o //
NK010(tha)021:270: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa la /
NK010(tha)021:271: gtor zlog dang 'brel na nyin tha mar zor lam
NK010(tha)021:272: dbye ba nas bzung 'phang ba'i las yan chad sngon
NK010(tha)021:273: du byas nas las mtha' mnan pas bsdu ba'i tshul
NK010(tha)021:274: / zor dang hom dang mnan pa dang //
NK010(tha)021:275: tha mas las su grub pa yin //
NK010(tha)021:278: gang du byed pa gru gsum brus //
NK010(tha)021:279: e yi tshogs kyi gzhal yas bskyed //
NK010(tha)021:280: stobs po che yi thugs ka nas //
NK010(tha)021:281: dzahls lcags kyus dgug cing bstim //
NK010(tha)021:282: thod pa'i nang du sbas nas ni //
NK010(tha)021:283: stobs po che yi phur pas gdab //
NK010(tha)021:284: rgya gram mnan cing las bzhis brdung //
NK010(tha)021:285: gang la byas kyang the tshom med //
NK010(tha)021:286: ces pa ltar lto 'phye la mi gnod pa'i cho gas dong tshad dang ldan pa brus la /
NK010(tha)021:287: dgra 'dre so so'i lteb tshul gyi r+au pa rang snod du bcug /
NK010(tha)021:288: tshon skud sngo dmar gyis dkris /
NK010(tha)021:289: phung res gtums la mnan sar sleb pa dang /
NK010(tha)021:290: gzhi bdag dang klu la dkar gtor bsngosa rjes /
NK010(tha)021:291: mnan dong gshin rje nag po'i lto bar bsams pa'i nang du mnan chas bskyur la /
NK010(tha)021:296: dur g.yam la stong rgya bris pas bkab pa'i steng phur pa gcig stobs po cher bsams la gzir /
NK010(tha)021:298: sri can bsgral ba'i zhing yin te //
NK010(tha)021:299: sangs rgyas bstan pa khyod kyis bshig /
NK010(tha)021:300: dkon mchog dbu 'phang khyod kyis smad //
NK010(tha)021:301: dge la rgyab kyi phyogs pa khyod //
NK010(tha)021:302: yon bdag rnams la gnod pa byas //
NK010(tha)021:303: sngags 'chang rnams kyi sku la bsdos //
NK010(tha)021:304: tshe rabs snga ma'i lan chags pa //
NK010(tha)021:305: sdang ba'i dgra dang gnod pa'i sri //
NK010(tha)021:307: nor gyi dogs nas ming rus 'di //
NK010(tha)021:308: rdo rje khro bo 'khor bcas kyi //
NK010(tha)021:309: zil gyis gnon pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK010(tha)021:311: sri can 'di las tshe ring med //
NK010(tha)021:312: tsha ba'i dbal dang gson gyi bdud //
NK010(tha)021:313: gshin gyi lcags su che ba'i sri //
NK010(tha)021:314: chung sri rgyal blon dmangs kyi sri //
NK010(tha)021:315: rje khol zhang tsha tsha yi sri //
NK010(tha)021:316: pha sri bu sri nu bo'i sri //
NK010(tha)021:317: dgra sri dme sri phung ba'i sri //
NK010(tha)021:318: dur sri god sri sgo sri rnams //
NK010(tha)021:319: sri can ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)021:320: dpal chen khro bo'i skur bsgoms nas //
NK010(tha)021:321: thams cad rdul du brlag par bya //
NK010(tha)021:322: rdo rje gzhon nu'i phur bu bstan //
NK010(tha)021:323: gshin rje nag po'i lto bar gzhug /
NK010(tha)021:324: ya ma r+aa dza'i zas su sbyin //
NK010(tha)021:325: ma mo rnams la mchod par 'bul //
NK010(tha)021:327: ri rab chen po'i rmang du sba //
NK010(tha)021:328: gshin rje'i bu yi lag tu gtad //
NK010(tha)021:329: rgya mtsho chen po'i gting du bskyur //
NK010(tha)021:330: mtshon chen 'bar ba'i rtse mos bcad //
NK010(tha)021:331: rdo rje phur pa'i dbal gyis gdab //
NK010(tha)021:332: ye shes rnon po'i rtse la gtad //
NK010(tha)021:334: nyung dkar sel med 'bem du gzugs //
NK010(tha)021:335: gu gul sbyar ba'i dud pas bdug /
NK010(tha)021:336: dug gi gtor mas myos su 'jug /
NK010(tha)021:337: lcags phye zangs phye'i dbal gyis gcad //
NK010(tha)021:338: gtun khung rdo rje tho bas brdung //
NK010(tha)021:339: khro bo rol pa'i tshogs su dbul //
NK010(tha)021:340: dgra bgegs snying la snying gzer gdab //
NK010(tha)021:341: byang chub sems ni ma skyes bar //
NK010(tha)021:342: nam yang btang bar mi bya'o //
NK010(tha)021:345: sa dang me chu'i rgyas 'debs spel rjes /
NK010(tha)021:346: steng du lag pa lu gu rgyud du bro brdung /
NK010(tha)021:350: shes brjod sogs spyi ltar bya ba nyid do //
